README FOR THE TSUNG_WRAPPER


Overview

The wrapper enables a series of YAML files which are fragments to be read and compiled into one tsung XML config file 
which can then be piped into tsung.


Explanation of folders:

environments
	This folder contains a yaml file for each environment
		- development
		- test
		- staging
		- live 

	or any other environment that you care to create.

	It will hold details for standard gobal environment variables to be loaded.
	The environment is determined by passing the -e flag to the wrap.rb program; development is assumed.

scenarios
	This folder contains a yaml file for each scenario to be tested.  It basically just requires a load of snippets.


snippets
	This folder contains snippets that can be included in various scenarios.


